{
  "id": "RAW_794bc9fe",
  "title": "2026 年，腾讯正式用元宝派杀入了 AI 社交。",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMzA5NjEyMA==&mid=2647679237&idx=1&sn=0a8e3f143e4ba4f4e1fa7ebae27abcb1",
  "date": "2026-01-27 01:32:00",
  "author": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "siteName": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">劲爆的东西来了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2026年开年，腾讯正式进军AI社交赛道。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">元宝直接一个大更新，开启了一个前所未有的玩法内测。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">名字叫做，元宝派。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">现在你不仅可以和朋友们在元宝里水群。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">跟群友一起，花式艾特元宝。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">甚至可以，装成别的大模型和元宝对话。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6777777777777778\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"4589\" data-height=\"3110\" data-imgfileid=\"500195559\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c80a8fad&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURpoGKdw8HgPwsn8Fcx4CE7JsCmMiaJT3o94fptUyDKHjgLyCB5X3wniaZ0iaHJXAvZrAVz6HFWuw3oSw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">说实话我真的没想到，大家进了元宝派的第一件事就是把自己的名字和头像改成各种大模型，导致我这个派的封面都变成了AI巨头开会。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">果然出门在外，身份都是自己给的。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">上面这几个派都是我建的，昨天拿到内测之后，太激动了，直接原地建了4个派。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当场在各个群里发邀请链接，几乎就是十几分钟就全部干到100人上限，大家也是库库水群，派里的群消息一会不看，就能直接就干到了99+。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">太吓人了，比微信群还活跃。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5370370370370371\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500195561\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=35d29158&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURpoGKdw8HgPwsn8Fcx4CE7JaHwV5aNcJEwoq73gSFXjBV7LB6bg2bk8w8BVjyHTWbHwPYicxJXSN0g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还有很多朋友跟我说，想玩，立刻想进，急急急急急急急急。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不过呢，没玩到的朋友也不用急，加入元宝派的方式其实非常简单。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">先把元宝更新到最新版本，如果你被灰度到了，就能看到底部多出来一个功能栏，左边第二个，就是元宝派。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4046296296296296\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1179\" data-height=\"477\" data-imgfileid=\"500195562\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=253a0bfe&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURpoGKdw8HgPwsn8Fcx4CE7JG4eDtdKl2YkjiaiaYBia8hQ09ibWmgtAQImTAlaicchxCHiaIcnlzU3uMxuQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">点进这个派，就可以通过右上角的加号来创建元宝派、邀请朋友进群了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5166666666666667\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1179\" data-height=\"609\" data-imgfileid=\"500195563\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a2a25440&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURpoGKdw8HgPwsn8Fcx4CE7J6JQDAr0SqEnATMxPjm2bFcytoc0kOCfmhdbYOm56eHPPpN1COdabCg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">没被灰度到也没关系，找你被灰度到的好基友给你发邀请链接，你就可以直接加入你朋友的派。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这里为了让你们看明白流程，我用我同事的手机给你们演示一下，没被灰度到的朋友们要怎么进入元宝派。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">先是点一下发在微信群里的这个元宝派链接，你就会来到一个邀请界面。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">再点一下加入元宝派，就能自动从微信跳转到元宝派的界面，然后你就会看到，你已经加入了该派，可以开始聊天了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.687962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"4589\" data-height=\"3155\" data-imgfileid=\"500195564\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d240322a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURpoGKdw8HgPwsn8Fcx4CE7JEz16zwoEhXKicV36LiaK9BYTzg1s6RGnpBkrhhlQSUxD73TLselXmyicQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">元宝派把微信和QQ都打通了，也就是说，你把一个链接分别发给微信和QQ好友，就能把他们拉进同一个群。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">QQ和微信分开这么多年，没想到这回在元宝里，天下一统了。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">至于元宝派的聊天界面本身，我们每个人应该都非常熟悉了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">微信群和QQ群里面最常用到的功能这里也都有，你可以发文字，发语音，传文件，传图片，引用撤回这些也不在话下。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还可以跟朋友音视频聊天，共享屏幕，用的都是腾讯会议的能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">上手属实没啥门槛，我就不做太多介绍了，因为只要你用过微信和QQ，你基本上就能在没有任何说明提示的情况下，毫无障碍地使用元宝派。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">有一个小细节要说一下，就是元宝派里，所有成员的头像都是在聊天框底部显示的，像这样。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.39444444444444443\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1179\" data-height=\"465\" data-imgfileid=\"500195566\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c027010e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURpoGKdw8HgPwsn8Fcx4CE7JhdgeQc10MKfKiawvrl1Kic4NFd2yVibthqpXbXpMDU4tnrlPWTND1ia0LQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">点开一个人的头像就可以跟他私聊。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还挺有意思的，不知道为啥，想起了当年高中读书的时候，给朋友传小纸条。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.025925925925926\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"4235\" data-height=\"4344\" data-imgfileid=\"500195567\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8f0ca1dc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURpoGKdw8HgPwsn8Fcx4CE7J7utYNEUgea1icUdASwriarhWN3xKfVXymHoy0ayl4ibySPCuepic0EJhcA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而在元宝派里，元宝也终于完整了，他那个贱不喽嗖的性格，也被发挥到了极致。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">之前在微信或者QQ里面，我一直觉得元宝的功能是很碎片的。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而现在，在这个派里，能做的事情就挺多的了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就拿微信上面没法实现的生图功能来说吧。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">现在你可以直接点开聊天框下面这一行中元宝的头像。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.39444444444444443\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1179\" data-height=\"465\" data-imgfileid=\"500195570\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ae482e8b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURpoGKdw8HgPwsn8Fcx4CE7JoyOgdaw7Ric9jhgvD0ZfugBswOUO1nXAxy1vBXiatzKxKAlfm7ah9BEw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后和元宝开小窗聊天，让元宝帮你生成一堆好玩的表情包图片。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0333333333333334\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"4235\" data-height=\"4378\" data-imgfileid=\"500195572\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f7475b2b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURpoGKdw8HgPwsn8Fcx4CE7JaM1C0rmic11rj5OrEcCHkEOfHh5tfJxvNgs2qBrsZKgsAs7OWMJtiaLQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而且应该是用的昨天刚刚迭代了图生图能力的混元图像3.0的模型，用嘴编辑的效果观感上，比之前牛逼了太多太多了，相当的牛逼。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这些图你可以直接保存下来发到派里。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还可以直接用群友的图来斗图。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如下面这个群友直接在群里艾特元宝，让元宝生成一堆我给粉丝买Mac mini的图。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">第一张图生成完他觉得不满意，又继续艾特元宝，让我本人出镜。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当然，因为他没有放我的参考图，所以这上面的卡兹克比我真人帅了亿点点。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4842592592592593\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"4590\" data-height=\"2221\" data-imgfileid=\"500195573\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d2e69484&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURpoGKdw8HgPwsn8Fcx4CE7JeiamWOJ6zbmwYlOVEmh081yZRo8johDiafqFDibyRvIbK3uBeRDmuK2rQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还可以点右下角的这个小图标，点开直接开启图片二创，实现表情包自由。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5203703703703704\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"4590\" data-height=\"2388\" data-imgfileid=\"500195574\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8244faf1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURpoGKdw8HgPwsn8Fcx4CE7Jpib83cc5MeoMulSTErKye4642iaDSwbCWEomt8u6f1567mZfibXtvqn1g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你还可以，用元宝来水群。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如，让它锐评你的游戏战绩，并给你讲一些游戏攻略。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6675925925925926\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"4590\" data-height=\"3065\" data-imgfileid=\"500195575\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8d4c2beb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURpoGKdw8HgPwsn8Fcx4CE7JSUTh30DtlQ4iaSG9RFESe1jtplzuxZq0qH2NibfbN68M2c2XNFMrOvWQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">或者只是纯粹地和它斗嘴，聊一些伦理梗，它也会接招。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个贱嗖嗖的性格之前还真没怎么见过，聊起来有一种神奇的魔力，是在是太贱了，说真的没想到他是这样的元宝。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5148148148148148\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"4590\" data-height=\"2361\" data-imgfileid=\"500195576\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=41595c1c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURpoGKdw8HgPwsn8Fcx4CE7JBu6QP8V8vTKelWIFiadxbmjICbo4HxUlTqYPc7uXMlL77tviaYMWyTCw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">它亲口，喊了我一句父王。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">那可是父王哎！</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">如果群消息叠的太多了，你还可以艾特元宝让它帮你总结消息。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span text